320	374	news	0c094c22-4961-49de-9465-d14d923869f0	{"id":"0c094c22-4961-49de-9465-d14d923869f0","category":"announcement","title":"IT-TODAY HACKTODAY 2026 Resmi Dimulai","slug":"hacktoday-2026-dimulai","excerpt":"9 tim dari 4 universitas bersaing selama 24 jam membangun solusi teknologi dalam dua track: AI dan Web.","content":"IT-TODAY HACKTODAY 2026 resmi dimulai pukul 08.00 WIB dengan kick-off ceremony di Auditorium Andi Hakim Nasoetion. Sebanyak 9 tim dari 4 universitas akan bersaing selama 24 jam penuh dalam dua track: AI Track dan Web Development Track.\\n\\nSesi presentasi dan penjurian dijadwalkan pada pukul 14.00 WIB hari ini.","is_published":true,"published_at":"2026-03-29T16:20:17.540Z","created_at":"2026-03-30T10:20:17.540Z","updated_at":"2026-04-04T18:04:58.042Z"}	{"thumbnail":"f3ee7335-334b-48d2-88cd-27a2332c0157"}	\N	\N
