8e1c5629-9640-4ca6-8118-95d1ebb71e12	f1ae03a9-c7a2-480b-a2af-cdba203a5636	IPB BADMINTON CUP 2026	ipb-badminton-2026	sport	active	2026-04-13	2026-04-16	GOR Badminton IPB	The IPB Badminton Cup is a premier regional tournament showcasing the finest student-athletes in the sport. Following the BWF standard for match officiating and equipment.	\N	https://ipb.link/join-event-2026	https://ipb.link/guidebook-2026	https://instagram.com/ipbuniversity	https://lucky.ipb.ac.id	t	f	2026-04-14 09:38:05.033091+00	2026-04-14 10:53:06.717419+00	2026-03-31 09:38:05.03+00	63af6c9b-ef38-4211-aada-36d458b1cd82	5a96ff7d-7d52-4f64-a182-60bdc5c7526b	\N
229dca26-216f-4ba6-a544-e8821caba18e	f1ae03a9-c7a2-480b-a2af-cdba203a5636	IPB BERLARI 2026	ipb-berlari-2026	sport	active	2026-04-09	2026-04-09	Kampus Dramaga	IPB BERLARI 2026 hadir sebagai perayaan semangat hidup sehat, kebersamaan, dan energi positif di lingkungan kampus IPB University. Lebih dari sekadar ajang olahraga, acara ini menjadi wadah bagi mahasiswa, dosen, tenaga kependidikan, hingga masyarakat umum untuk bergerak bersama, menikmati suasana, dan membangun gaya hidup aktif di tengah kesibukan akademik.\n\nDiselenggarakan di kawasan hijau dan asri kampus IPB, IPB BERLARI 2026 menawarkan pengalaman lari yang menyegarkan dengan rute yang dirancang khusus melewati berbagai titik ikonik kampus. Peserta akan disuguhkan kombinasi jalur yang menantang sekaligus menyenangkan, mulai dari lintasan datar yang cocok untuk pemula hingga segmen yang menguji ketahanan bagi pelari berpengalaman. Dengan pilihan kategori seperti 3K Fun Run, 5K, dan 10K Race, acara ini terbuka untuk semua kalangan, tanpa memandang tingkat kemampuan.	\N	https://ipb.link/join-event-2026	https://ipb.link/guidebook-2026	https://instagram.com/ipbuniversity	https://lucky.ipb.ac.id	t	f	2026-04-14 09:38:05.193965+00	2026-04-15 09:05:25.410357+00	2026-03-30 09:38:05.191+00	c5cc9b39-b8ba-4432-8293-fffedbd19bc1	e44375da-f618-4c76-8a0d-10ade71751f0	https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gACOQCxUrqE
2f6b7d6d-e631-4a02-9324-66395cd2dbf9	f1ae03a9-c7a2-480b-a2af-cdba203a5636	IPB FUTSAL CUP 2026	ipb-futsal-2026	sport	upcoming	2026-04-29	2026-05-09	GOR Futsal IPB	IPB FUTSAL CUP 2026 returns as one of the most anticipated intercollegiate sporting events of the year, bringing together passion, competition, and unity within the vibrant campus life of IPB University. This annual tournament is more than just a series of matches—it is a celebration of athleticism, teamwork, and the relentless spirit of student athletes who strive to represent their faculties and institutions with pride.\n\nHeld over the course of several thrilling days, IPB FUTSAL CUP 2026 gathers teams from various universities across Indonesia, creating a dynamic and highly competitive environment. Each match showcases not only technical skill and tactical discipline, but also the emotional intensity that defines futsal at its finest. From last-minute goals to dramatic penalty shootouts, every moment contributes to an unforgettable experience for players and spectators alike.\n\nThe tournament is hosted at IPB’s premier indoor sports facility, transformed into a lively arena filled with roaring supporters, colorful banners, and electrifying chants. Audiences can expect a professional-level event atmosphere, complete with live commentary, match statistics displays, and engaging halftime entertainment. The event also integrates modern elements such as social media coverage, live streaming, and interactive audience activities, ensuring accessibility and excitement for both on-site attendees and viewers from afar.	\N	https://ipb.link/reg-futsal-2026	https://ipb.link/guidebook-futsal-2026	https://instagram.com/ipbfutsalcup	https://futsal.ipb.ac.id	t	t	2026-04-14 09:38:05.863171+00	2026-04-14 10:52:45.52849+00	2026-04-26 09:38:05.861+00	7ce15dd5-2f26-476e-8a98-62f4c16d80e8	6188cf96-979b-4727-ad75-323dfe8d0006	\N
7a2ae16a-0b06-4705-aae3-1d95020899fa	f1ae03a9-c7a2-480b-a2af-cdba203a5636	IT-TODAY HACKTODAY 2026	hacktoday-2026	sport	active	2026-04-13	2026-04-14	Auditorium AHN	IT-TODAY HACKTODAY is IPB University's flagship technology competition. Indonesia's brightest young developers build high-tech solutions for local agricultural challenges.	\N	https://ipb.link/join-event-2026	https://ipb.link/guidebook-2026	https://instagram.com/ipbuniversity	https://lucky.ipb.ac.id	t	f	2026-04-14 09:38:05.573736+00	2026-04-14 10:52:54.8032+00	2026-03-25 09:38:05.571+00	ac1ae6b9-45bc-49d4-8e76-25c35adebe52	5abad252-da0a-4ba7-8d28-87a40e273792	\N
d4641459-b340-4e51-9263-ca61bf276c3d	f1ae03a9-c7a2-480b-a2af-cdba203a5636	FORKI X IPB 2026	forki-ipb-2026	sport	active	2026-04-12	2026-04-15	Gymnasium IPB Dramaga	FORKI × IPB CUP 2026 is the premier inter-university karate championship hosted by UKM Karate IPB in official partnership with the Federation Olahraga Karate-Do Indonesia (FORKI) and under the direct supervision of Direktorat Kemahasiswaan IPB University. Now in its fifth consecutive edition, the tournament has grown from a regional campus competition into one of the most anticipated collegiate karate events in West Java, drawing athletes from over a dozen universities across the island. \n\nThe 2026 edition marks a milestone year — for the first time, the competition adopts the full World Karate Federation (WKF) electronic scoring system across all Kumite categories, bringing the officiating standard in line with national-level championships. Athletes compete across six disciplines: Kata Perorangan Putra, Kata Perorangan Putri, Kumite -60kg, Kumite -67kg, Kumite +67kg, and Kumite Beregu.\n\nContact Person:- Ginting: wa.me/0898475927494	\N	https://ipb.link/join-event-2026	https://ipb.link/guidebook-2026	https://instagram.com/ipbuniversity	https://lucky.ipb.ac.id	t	f	2026-04-14 09:38:04.829887+00	2026-04-14 16:37:52.210646+00	2026-03-30 09:38:04.825+00	deef17cc-eaa2-4271-a4f0-105f5cf97299	43b2e432-b944-4d20-a7a4-34f6e1c02e0e	\N
cf73b248-4985-400d-b248-9d9b7bcc4fb9	f1ae03a9-c7a2-480b-a2af-cdba203a5636	IPB ART FESTIVAL 2026	ipb-art-fest-2026	arts	active	2026-04-13	2026-04-15	Gedung Graha Widya Wisuda (GWW)	IPB ART FESTIVAL 2026 hadir sebagai ruang ekspresi kreatif yang merayakan keberagaman seni, imajinasi, dan kolaborasi di lingkungan IPB University. Event ini menjadi titik temu bagi para seniman muda, kreator, dan pecinta seni untuk menampilkan karya terbaik mereka sekaligus menikmati atmosfer festival yang penuh warna, inspirasi, dan kebebasan berekspresi.\n\nSelama penyelenggaraan, IPB ART FESTIVAL 2026 menghadirkan berbagai bentuk seni dalam satu rangkaian acara yang dinamis. Mulai dari pertunjukan musik, tari tradisional dan modern, teater, hingga pameran seni rupa seperti lukisan, ilustrasi, fotografi, dan instalasi interaktif—semuanya dirancang untuk memberikan pengalaman artistik yang kaya dan beragam. Setiap sudut venue akan dipenuhi karya dan penampilan yang merefleksikan perspektif unik para kreator muda.\n\nFestival ini tidak hanya menjadi ajang pertunjukan, tetapi juga wadah kolaborasi lintas disiplin. Mahasiswa dari berbagai fakultas dan komunitas seni bekerja sama menciptakan karya yang inovatif, menggabungkan elemen visual, suara, dan gerak menjadi satu kesatuan yang harmonis. Hal ini menjadikan IPB ART FESTIVAL 2026 sebagai simbol sinergi antara kreativitas dan kebersamaan.\n\nPengunjung juga dapat menikmati berbagai aktivitas interaktif, seperti workshop seni, live painting, open mic session, dan creative market yang menghadirkan produk-produk unik dari brand lokal dan karya mahasiswa. Tidak hanya sebagai penonton, setiap orang didorong untuk ikut terlibat, mencoba, dan mengekspresikan diri mereka secara langsung.	\N	https://ipb.link/join-event-2026	https://ipb.link/guidebook-2026	https://instagram.com/ipbuniversity	https://lucky.ipb.ac.id	t	f	2026-04-14 09:38:06.031601+00	2026-04-14 12:39:09.423497+00	2026-03-15 09:38:06.028+00	fd6826c6-7bee-4acc-8161-4db525ada353	99b530ad-8f01-4135-9a26-118a504bb091	\N
\.
